XT Version 1.0 :
-----------------------

XT is a library that converts XLE output into ENIAM format.

Install
-------

XT requires OCaml version 4.02.3 compiler
together with Xlib library version 3.2 or later.

In order to install type:

make install

by default, XT is installed in the 'ocamlc -where'/eniam directory.
you can change it by editing the Makefile.

In order to test library type:
make test
./test [OPTIONS] <filename>

By default XT looks for resources in /usr/share/eniam directory.
However this behaviour may be changed by setting end exporting ENIAM_RESOURCE_PATH
environment variable.

